{"title":"git_lifecycle_markdown","type":"markdown","params":{"fontSize":10,"markdown":"This panel provides a quick view of the lifecycle of the top 25 git repositories by activity and authors for a given period of time.

## Definition

**Active**: at least 1 commit per month

## Charts

* Evolution of the number of active repositories during selected period of time, and its trend
* Top 25 git repositories by number of commits for selected period of time, showing level of activity by month
* Top 25 git repositories by number of *active* authors for selected period of time, showing level of active authors by month"},"aggs":[]}
